

<div class="parts-def">
  <p>The <strong>case</strong> protects your components from outside hazards: dust, dander, wandering fingers, and more. When you're buying your first case you want to consider: <strong>form factor, airflow, cable management, side panels, material type, and bays and mount points.</strong></p>

</div>

<section class="section" id="cases">
  <h1 class="title">Cases</h1>

  <table class="table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Name</th>
        <th>
          <abbr title="color">Color</abbr>
        </th>
        <th>
          <abbr title="ext">Ext.</abbr>
        </th>
        <th>
          <abbr title="int">Int.</abbr>
        </th>
        <th>
          <abbr title="pow-supp">Power Supply</abbr>
        </th>
        <th>
          <abbr title="type">Type</abbr>
        </th>
        <th>
          <abbr title="price">Price</abbr>
        </th>
      </tr>
    </thead>


    <% @cases.each do |part| %>

    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>
           <strong><%= part.name %></strong>
        </td>

        <% part.specs.each do |spec| %>
          <td><%= spec.attribute_value %></td>

        <% end %>
      </tr>


    </tbody>

    <% end %>
  </table>
